- **Existence checks (lines 210–340):** ~130 lines — `if not X.exists(): errors.append(...)`. **14% of the file** is file-existence checks.
- **Text presence checks (lines 340–620):** ~280 lines — `if phrase not in text: errors.append(...)`. **31% of the file.**
