## (B) Shared Data Model / Schema

### B1. Workflow Artifact (the central data structure)

All fixtures share this `starting_artifact` shape:
```
{
  "workflow_uuid": "wf-{TIMESTAMP}-{slug}",   # stable identity, time-ordered
  "workflow_id": "<same as workflow_uuid>",   # v10 alias (must match)
  "workflow_type": "PLAN|BUILD|DEBUG|REVIEW|VERIFY",
  "state_root": ".cc10x",                     # must be ".cc10x" (validated)
  "plan_mode": "direct|execution_plan|decision_rfc",
  "verification_rigor": "standard|critical_path",
  "proof_status": "gaps_found|passed|human_needed",
  "traceability": {"requirements":[], "phases":[], "verification":[], "remediation":[]},
  "phase_cursor": "phase-1|phase-2|null|debug-investigate",
  "task_ids": {},
  "results": {},
  "intent": {"goal": "<string>"},
  "evidence": {},
  "quality": {"convergence_state": "pending|stable|needs_iteration"},
  "status_history": [],
  "remediation_history": []
}
```

### B2. Agent Contract Schemas (validated by replay checker)

- **Builder:** `STATUS, PHASE_ID, PHASE_STATUS, PHASE_EXIT_READY, CHECKPOINT_TYPE, PROOF_STATUS, INPUTS, EXPECTED_ARTIFACTS, TDD_RED_EXIT, TDD_GREEN_EXIT, BLOCKED_ITEMS, SKIPPED_ITEMS, SCOPE_INCREASES, SCENARIOS`
- **Verifier:** `SCENARIOS_TOTAL, SCENARIOS_PASSED, SCENARIOS_FAILED, SCENARIO_ROWS, EVIDENCE: {scenarios}`
- **Investigator:** `STATUS, TDD_RED_EXIT, TDD_GREEN_EXIT, BLAST_RADIUS_SCAN, VARIANTS_COVERED, VARIANTS_NOT_APPLICABLE, SCENARIOS, NEEDS_EXTERNAL_RESEARCH, RESEARCH_REASON`
