- **Plan Gap Reviewer:** `STATUS, BLOCKING_FINDINGS_COUNT, REPLAN_NEEDED, REPLAN_REASON, FINDING_BUCKETS, PLANNING_REVIEW_STATUS`

### B3. Plan DAG Model (validated by `validate_plan_dag`)

5-task dependency chain:
```
planner_create (plan-create) → 
  planning_review_pass1 (plan-review-gap-1) → 
    planner_replan (re-plan) → 
      planning_review_pass2 (plan-review-gap-2) → 
        memory_finalize (memory-finalize)
```
Each task has `{phase, status, blockedBy[]}`. Statuses: `completed|pending|deleted`.

### B4. Scenario Row Schema (shared across all contracts)

```
{name, given, when, then, command, expected, actual, exit_code, status}
```
- `status`: `PASS|FAIL`
- `exit_code`: integer (0 = pass)
- Used by builder, verifier, investigator contracts

### B5. Benchmark Output Schemas (worldclass benchmark only)

- Inventory, delta register, bakeoff, benchmark rows, claim scoreboard — all JSON + markdown pairs in `docs/benchmarks/`
- No schema validation on outputs — just `json.dumps(indent=2)`

### B6. Live Harness Manifest Schema (live harness runner)

